nodes.text: Duanna Falos was a female individual who had a reputation for being a fearless hunter. At some point during galactic history, Falos traveled to the planet Durace in the Unknown Regions along with her lover, her bodyguard and her Mon Calamari servant, because she wanted to test her skills by hunting the planet's beasts. On arrival on the world, she hired a group of agents to take her and her party on a hunt, but as their expedition progressed, the group experienced a series of accidents and the agents realized that one of Falos' associates was trying to kill her.
